o pečlivý úklid všech školních prostor.

1189
01:29:41,990 --> 01:29:43,610
<i>Ano!

1190
01:29:58,300 --> 01:29:59,360
Proč jsi tady?

1191
01:30:06,100 --> 01:30:07,090
